The bbq spring chicken was delicious. After reading the review about waiting time. I asked the seller how long was it and turned out to be just 15 mins and I went for it. And it was delicious. Well marinated, spring chicken was juicy. Chilli sauce was well done and not too spicy and sharp. Will buy again and check waiting time in advance.
